<item>
            <title>[WICKET-6310] Once invalidated the Session will be invalidated on every detach</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6310</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve created a simple project to show that I&apos;ve a test which works in Wicket 7 but is failing in Wicket 8. Its a simple login form which authenticates a user with Spring Security.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In Wicket 8 the user is redirected to the LoginPage after a succesul login without an error. In Wicket 7 the user is redirected to the HomePage as expected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can change the version in the maven property section. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve tried to debug by myself but I didn&apos;t found anything...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hint: The test is working in Wicket 8 if you redirect the page with setResponsePage(new HomePage.class) instead of setResponsePage(Homepage.class)&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
